name: The Moon, The Crocobear And the Fireplace

metadata.name: Head in the Dark
metadata.description:
As the legend goes, those most spiritually and visually charged photographic works of my students are bound to escape the threadmill of retouching and elevate the froth of the daydream to bounce into the upper levels of the atmosphere also known as the Ether.
And there, discovered by the Collectors, get rid of the blockchains holding them to pave their ways into the most stunning private collections.

All the coins go directly to fellow photographers, no middleman. A unique opportunity to show your love and support.
